      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved potatoes</strong> to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, cook for 12-15 min or until fork-tender, then drain and return to the pot and keep covered until later</p>",
