    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Grate the <strong>apple<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>(skin on) and discard the core<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Cut the <strong>cucumber </strong>in half lengthways, scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon and discard</p><p>Grate the <strong>deseeded</strong> <strong>cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
