            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with matching lid) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1629798926603-x200.jpg",
