            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the potatoes have started to brown, add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan with a splash of <strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 1-2 min or until wilted</p><p>Grate the <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1629798967916-x200.jpg",
