            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the greens have wilted, crack the<strong> eggs</strong> over the potatoes, sprinkle over the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and cook, covered, for 3-4 min or until the eggs are cooked through and the cheese has melted – these are your<strong> cheesy gochujang potatoes with fried egg</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime </strong>into wedges</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
