            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheesy gochujang potatoes with fried egg </strong>with the<strong> tangy slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, <strong>toasted sesame seeds </strong>and a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
